title: Tom Petty - Southern Accents In The Sunshine States (2015)
description:
There were a lot of bootleg recordings from this legendary show out there over the years - this official release is the most complete. But the source is the same: SBD FM - not a desirable SBD Pre-FM. Thatfore this recording has not the full frequency range - it's cut off at around 16-18kHz (I added some analysis files). maxblues


Tom Petty & The Heartbreakers - Southern Accents In The Sunshine State
Label: Gossip - GOSS018
Format: 2 x CD, Album, Compilation
Country: US
Released: 2015
Genre: Rock

Recorded from an FM broadcast live from the Stephen C O'Connell Center, Gainesville, FL, November 4, 1993
